[p 
	"Decided to try to submit this movie, although I'm feeling a bit uncertain since this is my first run starting from SRAM, and there's also something dubious about the rom choice. Please don't bite too hard if something's amiss.
	$LF
]p
[p 
	[a class=extlink href=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VzwNDAImsrE rel=nofollow 
		"Here's what this run should look like through your emulator, i.e. an unofficial Youtube encode.
	]a
	$LF
]p
[p 
	[a class=extlink href=http://dehacked.2y.net/microstorage.php/info/1702231179/Mortal%20Kombat%20-%20Tournament%20Edition%20%28U%29%20%28M5%29%20%5BhI%5D%20verification.vbm rel=nofollow 
		"Verification movie, probably needed.
	]a
