	]a
	": Like most other hand-held Mortal Kombat ports, this one is also poorly designed. The run itself tries to make the best of the game, but there isn't much to deliver. Taking damage without it being funny or unexpected also makes this run seem less like a TAS and more like a regular speedrun. I let this run simmer for a couple of days hoping for more turnout on comments, but there doesn't seem to be much interest. Therefore, rejecting.
